{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-situations-page-tsx","path":"/en/situations/free-movement-people/gatherings","result":{"data":{"situation":{"title":"Gatherings","meta_description":"Rules for organizing demonstrations, restrictions on the number of people and hygiene measures.","content":{"processed":"<h2><strong>Rules and Recommendations</strong></h2>\n<p>The government's measures restricted the right of the people peaceably to assemble.</p>\n<p>If you want to demonstrate or to organize a demonstration, there <strong>must not be more than 100 participants</strong>. It is necessary to retain small <strong>clusters at most 20</strong> <strong>people</strong> and keep the distance at least <strong>2 meters</strong> between the clusters. All participants of the demonstration must wear a face mask or other respiratory protection. Also, no indoor demonstrations are allowed.</p>\n"},"path":{"alias":"/situations/free-movement-people/gatherings"},"changed":"2020-12-03T15:51:47+00:00","valid_from":"2020-11-04T00:00:00+01:00","langcode":"en","created":"2020-11-04T23:45:51+00:00","links":[{"uri":"https://www.vlada.cz/assets/media-centrum/aktualne/hromadne-akce-1262.pdf","title":"Government measures on the free movement of persons"}],"relationships":{"region":[],"icon":{"code":"directions_walk"},"situation_type":{"name":"Free movement of people","path":{"alias":"/situations/free-movement-people"},"relationships":{"icon":{"code":"directions_walk"}}},"measures":[],"related_situations":[]},"questions_answers":[],"update":null,"valid_to":"2020-11-20T23:59:59+01:00","last_updated":"2020-11-18T22:14:00+01:00"},"situationArea":{"name":"Free movement of people","path":{"alias":"/situations/free-movement-people"},"relationships":{"icon":{"code":"directions_walk"},"situation":[{"id":"7ae65304-9098-5acd-a19f-973af8c793b7","title":"Measures on free movement","path":{"alias":"/situations/free-movement-people/measures-free-movement"}},{"id":"69089399-f5ce-52e0-ab8f-14e4500cc0